data.description: Come see this spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 3 car garage, located on an oversized corner lot. Large home boasting over 2400 heated sq ft, featuring a private Mother-in-Law suite. This open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living room, dining area and kitchen with beautiful light fixtures, fans and high ceilings. Tile flooring in the open areas and carpets in the bedrooms. The kitchen is beautifully designed with a walk around kitchen island, granite countertops, pantry, plenty of cabinets with tons of space, newer appliances and nook area. Large master bedroom with tray ceilings, walk in closet and private en-suite bathroom; all other bedrooms are just as spacious. Laundry room, Fenced yard and security system. Home is only a few years old located in the Pine Lakes subdivision near the golf course. Home is being sold "AS-IS"
